com.rjrudin.marklogic.mgmt

Class ManageClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rjrudin.marklogic.client.LoggingObject
      • com.rjrudin.marklogic.mgmt.ManageClient

  • public class ManageClient
extends com.rjrudin.marklogic.client.LoggingObject
    Wraps a RestTemplate with methods that should simplify accessing the Manage API with RestTemplate. Each NounManager should depend on an instance of ManageClient for accessing the Manage API.
